let profileListContainer = {
  height: "22px",
  display: "flex",
  width: "calc(65vw - 28px)",
  border: "1px solid #4382BC",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd",
  cursor: "default",
  textDecoration: "none", 
  color: "inherit"
}

let profileListContainerMain = {
  cursor: "pointer",
  fontSize: "15px",
  textAlign: "center",
  width: "200px",
  minWidth: "200px",
  maxWidth: "200px",
  color: "white",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  lineHeight: "22px",
  borderRadius: "4px 0px 0px 4px",
  textIndent: "1px"
}

let profileListContainerOther = {
  fontSize: "15px",
  width: "16.67%",
  textTransform: "capitalize",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  textOverflow: "ellipsis",
  lineHeight: "20px",
  textAlign: "center",
  cursor: "default"
}

export {
  profileListContainer,
  profileListContainerMain,
  profileListContainerOther
}
